'''Campus Violence Prevention Program (CVPP)'''
 
CVPP provides support for victims of sexual assault, domestic violence, stalking, and hate crimes. Confidential advocates relate to and deal with the experiences of victims. CVPP also provides sexual assault education through a volunteer peer-educator program. 
Rape Aggression Defense (RAD) is a women’s self-defense class that is       
administered by CVPP.

